  "logNo": "221172284936",
  "title": "감기의 정체를 알려다오 [남성역 소아 한의원] ",
  "addDate": "2017. 12. 27.",
  "categoryNo": "39",
  "parentCategoryNo": "9",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=221172284936",
  "html_size": 192941,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view221172284936\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea221172284936\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">요즘 우리 이수한의원에 내원하는 감기환자들이 늘어나고 있습니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">그래서\r\n오늘은 우리를 괴롭히는 감기의 정체에 대해서 알아보고 한방치료에 대해서도 알아보도록 하겠습니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">.</span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\"><br /></span></p><p align=\"center\" style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: center; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a15a7a420d5e5347.jpg\" width=\"243\" height=\"208\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 208px; rwidth: 243px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMjdfOSAg/MDAxNTE0MzYyOTAzNjQ4.uVzDfWVaoqaJZcTDBF4bHKY3jcWSFzMaLCPUTdrVrncg.N38pwuDupNOKKw_jy2Np4KqugKvNKcK_6BPszFC6C-Ag.JPEG.isuhani/%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337EE53E08')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a15a7a420d5e5347.jpg\"></span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\"><br /></span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">양방에서는 바이러스에 의한 상기도 감염으로 보는 감기</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">!! </span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">그렇다면 한의학에서는 감기를 어떻게 진단하고 치료할까요</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">? </span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">한의학에서 감기는 외부의 차가운 기운</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">寒邪</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">이 몸에 침입하면서 생기는 병으로</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">추위에 상하는 병이라는 의미로</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\"> '</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">상한</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">傷寒</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">)'</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">이라고 본답니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">흔히</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\"> '</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">감기</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">'</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">라고 부르는\r\n증상 중에 오한발열</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">惡寒發熱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">은 외부의 한사</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">寒邪</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">가 우리 몸의 표</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">表</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">에 침입했을 때 나타나는 증상입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">한사</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">寒邪</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">가 몸의 겉에서 안으로 깊숙이 침투할 수록 더 깊은 병이 되고\r\n다양한 증상들이 나타나게 됩니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">. </span></p><p align=\"center\" style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: center; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMjdfOTYg/MDAxNTE0MzYyOTg2NTg3.OTOTQ5e6aP37bsx7gI4wfJ7xbFXsoxH7BVpJShF2CzYg.EdVjz38OmC-I-7kSDnsXJ3-WViXawQsZLkL-WE_kzlAg.JPEG.isuhani/images.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"225\" height=\"224\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 224px; rwidth: 225px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMjdfOTYg/MDAxNTE0MzYyOTg2NTg3.OTOTQ5e6aP37bsx7gI4wfJ7xbFXsoxH7BVpJShF2CzYg.EdVjz38OmC-I-7kSDnsXJ3-WViXawQsZLkL-WE_kzlAg.JPEG.isuhani/images.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337EE53E08')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMjdfOTYg/MDAxNTE0MzYyOTg2NTg3.OTOTQ5e6aP37bsx7gI4wfJ7xbFXsoxH7BVpJShF2CzYg.EdVjz38OmC-I-7kSDnsXJ3-WViXawQsZLkL-WE_kzlAg.JPEG.isuhani/images.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">그러므로 한의학에서 감기 예방은 외부의 한사</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">寒邪</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">가 몸으로 침투하는 것을 막는 것이 중요합니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">한사</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">(</span><a name=\"_Hlk502139049\" class=\"con_link\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">寒</span></a><a name=\"_Hlk502140683\" class=\"con_link\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">邪</span></a><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">가 들어오기 쉬운\r\n목 뒤와 등 상부</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">피부를 가리고 따뜻하게 해서 차가운 기운에 상하지 않도록 하면 감기에 걸리지 않을\r\n것입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">다만 면역이 떨어져있고 약해져 있는 경우에는 약한 한사</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">寒邪</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">에도 상하기 쉬우므로 면역을 올리고 피부의 주리를 단단하게 하는 것도 중요합니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">.</span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: center; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8734b6e1e09f79d4.png\" width=\"257\" height=\"196\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 196px; rwidth: 257px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMjdfMjU5/MDAxNTE0MzYzMDY4MTk2.BaeyIhslNGZTxI4b8E03KwwyaZeX48PvHFlaiNsCIV0g.CdtpF0I2SwzUK59nWBkEJU0c_QE0GOJ2i1kWXzAW-u8g.PNG.isuhani/images.png\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337EE53E08')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8734b6e1e09f79d4.png\"></span></p><p align=\"center\" style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: center; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\"><br /></span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">감기의 치료는 한사</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">寒邪</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">를\r\n몰아내는 발산</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">發散</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">을 기본으로 합니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">소엽</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">계지</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">생강</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">강황 등으로 한기를 몰아내고 이외에 여기저기 쑤시는 몸살기운</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">발열</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">기침</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">콧물 등 각각의 증상에 맞는 약재들을 배합하여 처방합니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">. </span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">한방 감기치료는 양약과는 달리 증상의 호전에만 치중하지 않고 근본치료도 병행하기 때문에 좀더 안전하고 부작용없이\r\n감기를 치료할 수 있습니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">. </span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">다음 포스트에서는 감기를 예방하는 방법에 대해서 더 자세히 알아보도록 하겠습니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\">.&nbsp;</span></p><p style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\"><br /></span></p><p align=\"center\" style='margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: center; line-height: 2; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; font-size: 10pt;'><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 돋움, Dotum; font-size: 12pt;\"><video src=\"https://mblogvideo-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMjdfMjA5/MDAxNTE0MzYyOTQ0MTIx.-GW3cN-l_RE4UshdGoDvnooYnCyMmNh3dqVJJq0JkGwg.ThWbWUtcmdA_u0Of2y2arXNIjEf019Wgrpc7o7sNHE8g.GIF.isuhani/9340435261364715768.gif?type=mp4w800\" width=\"412\" height=\"335\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMjdfMjA5/MDAxNTE0MzYyOTQ0MTIx.-GW3cN-l_RE4UshdGoDvnooYnCyMmNh3dqVJJq0JkGwg.ThWbWUtcmdA_u0Of2y2arXNIjEf019Wgrpc7o7sNHE8g.GIF.isuhani/9340435261364715768.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337EE53E08')\" alt=\"\" loop=\"loop\" muted=\"muted\" playsinline=\"playsinline\" data-gif-url=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/98102d4f526724c8.gif\" class=\"_photoImage _gifmp4\">&nbsp;</video></span></p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
